metadata.name: Omen of the All-Seeing.
metadata.description:
Our artist finds a cryptic scripture that represents something that he has been struggling with - Self-Doubt. 

With the eye of disbelief creeping in, he questions his abilities and his purpose within a world that is brimming with saturation. Who is he supposed to be? Does his lessons account for something? Where is his destiny? 

As our protagonist struggles with the thoughts, he can't help but admire the flowing elements around the murals. Each representing a strength that dwells within him. Maybe eventually, he can use those to eliminate the self-doubt that haunts him? 

-- Crypt of a Wandering Artist --
